Position Description 
The incumbent will be responsible for assisting with academic human resources affairs in the Academic Administration Office at GTIIT. 

Duties and Responsibilities 
1. Provide support for implementing the administration procedure of teacher HR support, including salary calculation, contract terms explanation, employment contract preparation, orientation, etc;
2. Provide support for data entering for teachers;
3. Assist in Government reports related to academic members
4. Manage Government Data systems related to teachers;
5. Assist Head of Academic Administration Office on other projects as needed;
6. Complete other tasks assigned by superiors.

Required Job Specifications 
1. Required qualification: bachelor degree or above from an internationally reputable university; Accounting or HR major is preferred;
2. Required experience:1-2 years, working experience in HR is preferred.

Required Job Competencies 
1. Language ability: Fluent Chinese and English; 
2. Multi-task skills; 
3. Good Microsoft Office skills, especially Excel; 
4. Good planning and organizing skills; 
5. Good communication and collaboration skills;
6. Good interpersonal skill to work in an international, cross-cultural work environment.

一、工作内容;
1、负责发布职位信息，初步筛选简历，邀约候选人面试;
2、协助处理人事日常相关工作，包括培训、入离职办理等人事手续;
3、负责公司日常的考勤工作;
4、负责公司办公室管理以及餐厅日常管理工作;
5、负责日常办公用品采购，会议室安排工作；
6、领导交代的其他事务性工作。
二、任职要求
1、本科以上学历，2024年及以后毕业，有相关人事行政处理工作优先考虑；
2、每周一到周五可正常出勤;
3、有较强的亲和力，语言和文字表达能力、沟通能力和协调能力;
4、熟练使用办公软件。

